					"title": "<img src='img/water_security.png' hspace=10>Source Protection Explorer",
					"description": "Investing in watershed health is a sustainable way to enhance water security. The Source Protection Explorer enables users to explore cities that can meet specified pollution reduction targets using conservation actions and the area and cost required to reach these targets.",
